    <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-4">Vital Check: iTERVE's</h2>
    <p class="mb-2">Our AI scientists have put in the efforts to extract PPG waves and RGB using laptop/desktop webcams and derive values of key vitals such as blood pressure, heart rate, HRV, oxygen saturation, respiration rate, pulse respiratory quotient (PRQ), sympathetic stress, parasympathetic activity, and hemoglobin with high accuracy. As of now, we have tested the efficacy of heart rate (as shown in image) and oxygen saturation (SpO2) with accuracy of 99%.</p>
    <p class="mb-2">These are breakthrough results and will help in connecting rural/remote areas with self-care health support and advanced healthcare connecting primary healthcare/doctor/consultant based on self-care data wherever mobile network works.</p>
