    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">iMR: Intelligent Medical Record (Your Health Dashboard)</div>
<div class="mt-4 text-xl font-medium text-gray-800">About iMR</div>
<div class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-700">In today's scenario, doctors often struggle when comparing medical test reports manually. This method leads to numerous errors, as the human brain can only remember a limited amount of information. To solve this issue, we present the solution of an Intelligent Medical Record. This will allow doctors to easily view all previous medical test reports in a visually appealing and graphical manner. </div>
<div class="text-xl font-bold text-center my-8">How iMR works</div>
<div class="text-base text-gray-700 text-center my-4">
iMR converts all uploaded diagnostic test reports, prescriptions, and other medical records into a digitally readable format from PDF or image format, as uploaded by the user. The next step is to put all historical test data in a tabular format, including the vital tests done by iTERVE, and display it on the dashboard as a table and graphical form for easy understanding.
</div>
<div class="text-base text-gray-700 text-center my-4">
Our AI model detects any abnormal historical test data and highlights it, as well as linking it to the doctor's prescription/diagnostic report if any. This provides clear and accurate information to the physician/consultant, enabling them to diagnose more accurately and provide better treatment to the patient.
</div><hr>

  </div>
  <div class="text-center font-medium text-2xl">Personalized Nutrition</div>
<div class="text-center text-lg font-medium mt-2">YOUR PERSONALISED NUTRITIOUS REQUIREMENT AND SUGGESTED FOOD OPTIONS POWERED BY AI</div>
<div class="text-center font-medium text-xl mt-4">About Personalized Nutrition</div>
<p class="text-center mt-2">Proper nutrition fuels the body for optimal performance. Whether you want to bulk up, slim down, reverse disease, control symptoms, or optimize your health and longevity, iTERVE Personalized Nutrition and Meal Planning can help. The app pinpoints areas of needed improvement for your chosen goals and offers macro and micronutrient guidance for creating a balanced, nutrient-dense diet based on the foods you like to eat.</p>
<p class="text-center mt-2">What sets iTERVE apart from others is its amazing meal planning and personalized nutrition guidance. It empowers you to make nutrition work for you better. </p> <hr>






