  <p class="text-lg mb-4">Second AI model been built and trained to convert health records into a digitally readable format and prepare an intelligent medical record view for easy understanding of historical health along with highlighting any past abnormal conditions and connecting it with the respective diagnosis and prescription, if any.</p>
  <p class="text-lg">Third AI model provides accurate body needs for macro and micro nutrients based on your profile, which includes age, weight, physical activities, etc. and vitals along with historical health data attached to your profile.</p>
